                    <p>A clean, modern portfolio template for creative professionals.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="project-link">View Project</a>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <img src="project3.jpg" alt="Project 3">
                    <h3>Weather App</h3>
                    <p>Real-time weather application with 5-day forecast.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="project-link">View Project</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about" class="section">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <img src="profile.jpg" alt="Profile Picture" class="profile-img">
                <div class="bio">
                    <p>I'm a passionate web developer with 5 years of experience creating digital experiences. I specialize in front-end development with a focus on accessibility and performance.</p>
                    <p>When I'm not coding, you can find me hiking, reading sci-fi novels, or experimenting with new recipes in the kitchen.</p>
